# Code Owners - Automatic Review Assignments
#
# This file defines code ownership and automatic review assignments.
# Users or teams mentioned here will automatically be requested for review
# when someone opens a pull request that modifies matching files.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> @username @org/team
# Patterns follow .gitignore rules (glob patterns)
# Later matches override earlier ones

# Repository Owner - Default for everything
